# cortex-agent-generator — environment variable template
#
# REAL SECRETS MUST NOT go here. This file is a template only.
# Actual secrets are loaded from /opt/cortexos/.secrets/ files at runtime.
#
# Copy the variable NAMES below into the appropriate .secrets/ file and fill in real values.

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Server
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Optional. Port the WS sidecar listens on. Default: 3082
# GENERATOR_PORT=3082

# Optional. Allowed WebSocket origin (e.g. https://cortexos.tailfd052e.ts.net).
# If empty, origin check is skipped (not recommended for production).
# ALLOWED_ORIGIN=

# Optional. Max age (ms) before re-checking admin group membership. Default: DEFAULT_ROLE_CHECK_MAX_AGE_MS from @cortexos/session-auth
# GENERATOR_ROLE_CHECK_MAX_AGE_MS=

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Database
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Required. PostgreSQL connection string used by the session-auth pool.
# Example: postgres://dashboard:<password>@127.0.0.1:5432/cortex_dashboard
# DATABASE_URL=

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 9router / LLM gateway
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# The API key and base URL for the 9router LLM proxy are read at runtime
# from /opt/cortexos/.secrets/9router.env (NOT from process environment).
# Keys in that file:
#   NINEROUTER_API_KEY   — bearer key for the 9router API (required)
#   NINEROUTER_BASE_URL  — base URL of the 9router proxy (default: http://127.0.0.1:11434)
